Package com.google.ads.mediation

Interface Summary
MediationAdapter<ADDITIONAL_PARAMETERS,SERVER_PARAMETERS extends MediationServerParameters> A MediationAdapter exposes methods that the mediation library can use to control a mediated ad network's SDK.
MediationBannerAdapter<ADDITIONAL_PARAMETERS extends NetworkExtras,SERVER_PARAMETERS extends MediationServerParameters> A MediationBannerAdapter exposes methods that the mediation library can use to control a mediated ad network's SDK for Banner Ads.
MediationBannerListener A MediationBannerListener object provides a mechanism for an adapter to communicate back to the mediation library.
MediationInterstitialAdapter<ADDITIONAL_PARAMETERS extends NetworkExtras,SERVER_PARAMETERS extends MediationServerParameters> A MediationInterstitialAdapter exposes methods that the mediation library can use to control a mediated ad network's SDK for interstitial ads.
MediationInterstitialListener A MediationInterstitialListener object provides a mechanism for an adapter to communicate back to the mediation library.
NetworkExtras A NetworkExtras object contains information set by the publisher on the client device.
 

Class Summary
EmptyNetworkExtras An empty network extras.
MediationAdRequest A MediationAdRequest object contains information about the ad to fetch for a single publisher.
MediationServerParameters A MediationServerParameters object contains information set by the publisher on the mediation back-end servers.
 

Exception Summary
MediationServerParameters.MappingException An Exception thrown when there was an issue with mapping.
